name: Quadglide f4
tagline: Just another flight controller for racing multirotors
body:
### Welcome to QuadGlideF4 flight controller GitHub Pages.
***

I started to design the QuadGlideF4 just to learn more how a flight controller works and get one that would fit my needs.
Also a wanted one that is robust and will not break if have have a ESC fire or reverse the battery polarity. It will not implement any new functions that are not already out there. For now I'm using KISS ESC so it will have a 1-wire bus to get telemetry.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
